			<description><![CDATA[<p>
GetYourGuide.com, an online booking website for tours and activities, is one of the fastest growing startups in travel. From bus sightseeing in London to shark diving in Cape Town, our goal is nothing short of making every tour &amp; activity in the world bookable for travelers everywhere. Our partners include TripAdvisor, Opodo, STA Travel and many more.</p>
<p>
We&#39;re looking for smart, inspired people to join our international team in the heart of Berlin. If you want to take a front seat in shaping the trajectory of a young company, GetYourGuide is the place for you.</p>
<p>
Tasks include but are not limited to:</p>
<p>
Responsible for the company&rsquo;s PR activities (product and corporate communications)<br />
Overseeing and coordinating network of PR agencies in Germany, the UK, and the USA<br />
Developing and implementing the company&rsquo;s media strategies<br />
Dealing with enquiries from the public, the press, and related organizations<br />
Organizing the company&rsquo;s presence at events (trade shows, conferences, etc.)<br />
Role reports directly to the CEO<br />
Requirements:</p>
<p>
At least 3 years&rsquo; work experience in a media and communication-related profession<br />
German on a native level<br />
English on a near-native speaker level<br />
Outgoing and open personality<br />
Extensive experience writing press releases<br />
Passion for travel and Internet-related publishing<br />
Excellent communication skills to explain and implement your decisions<br />
College degree or equivalent experience<br />
Why join us?</p>
<p>
Highly motivated team in a high-growth environment<br />
Large responsibilities from day one and flat hierarchies<br />
Opportunity to lead all PR activities of GetYourGuide<br />
Pizza Fridays with beer from 6pm and other start-up perks<br />
How to apply:</p>
<p>
Please send us your CV and a letter of motivation and include short answers to the following questions:</p>
<p>
Why would you like to work at GetYourGuide and not somewhere else?</p>
<p>
Please write a fictional press release for GetYourGuide announcing a major change to the company. Provide versions in English and German, and be creative!</p>
<p>
We&#39;re a fun, thriving startup with a great work environment and plenty of growth in our future. If we&#39;ve piqued your interest, drop us an email with your resume and motivation letter and we&rsquo;ll talk.</p>
<p>
Apply now</p>
